{"tid":1632110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"俾人扑爛左架搵食車偷晒啲錢！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:06.000Z","uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae4e6f8dc567101043ee36dba6d54ec1d8bfd12","tid":1632110,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"好唔開心，發完夢返黎見到辛辛苦苦搵返黎既錢無晒，想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46e7bd21ad11942271882978269b22da6661c15","tid":1632110,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"1b805830376685bfa7a0d38c4d12f01636c884f8","tid":1632110,"uid":189600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"有幾多錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3be75448464e25634c45e580befb27b9f4e738","tid":1632110,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ae4e6f8dc567101043ee36dba6d54ec1d8bfd12","tid":1632110,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"好唔開心，發完夢返黎見到辛辛苦苦搵返黎既錢無晒，想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:54.000Z","msg":"唔係保險CLAIM番咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b6ab5bf87ff7f060d214c194410f8747831777","tid":1632110,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b805830376685bfa7a0d38c4d12f01636c884f8","tid":1632110,"uid":189600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"有幾多錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:06.000Z","msg":"我都想知"}]}